**Verifier Checklist**

* [ ] Walrus CID is retrievable
* [ ] SL attestation is valid & unexpired
* [ ] Intent not expired; nullifier unseen
* [ ] Counterparty proofs present and match
* [ ] Atomic co‑sign present before settlement
